/foreign>, etc.), <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">γραφάς, εὐθύνας, εἰσαγγελίας, πάντα ταῦτ᾽ ἐπαγόντων μοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:249\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.249</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg015.perseus-grc1:3:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.2</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg016.perseus-grc1:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.12</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}